1
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:49,119
Lookkai.

2
00:00:49,760 --> 00:00:51,440
Why did Khun Pakin
ask me to come here?

3
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:52,880
This is a cliff.

4
00:00:59,719 --> 00:01:00,840
Hello, Venus

5
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:03,559
Are you glad to see me?

6
00:01:04,039 --> 00:01:04,840
Aunt Khae?

7
00:01:05,719 --> 00:01:06,159
Lookkai.

8
00:01:06,599 --> 00:01:07,360
What is going on?

9
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:08,760
Didn't you tell me

10
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:10,360
that Khun Pakin
would be waiting for me here?

11
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,199
P'Dao.

12
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,400
I'm sorry.

13
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,880
If I didn't obey my mom

14
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,119
she threatened to kill everyone.

15
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:22,079
And then kill herself.

16
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:25,079
I still don't understand

17
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,599
what is all this about?

18
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:27,280
Unless

19
00:01:27,719 --> 00:01:28,119
That's right.

20
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:30,440
It was all my doing.

21
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,039
When I heard the news

22
00:01:32,039 --> 00:01:32,960
that someone committed suicide

23
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:34,039
because of Saturn,

24
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:36,559
Dao Kang Fah was so paranoid.

25
00:01:36,559 --> 00:01:38,199
Terrified that her grandson
would get in trouble,

26
00:01:38,199 --> 00:01:39,440
she ordered a cover up.

27
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,639
That's when I saw the
perfect opportunity.

28
00:01:40,639 --> 00:01:42,000
to finally succeed.

29
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:47,360
You have to trust me, Saturn.

30
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,480
We are family.

31
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,400
Run away abroad for a while.

32
00:01:53,079 --> 00:01:54,760
Once things quiet down, you can come back.

33
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,519
Okay?

34
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,519
Trust me.

35
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:07,079
And where is Saturn right now?

36
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,960
I told you, he went abroad

37
00:02:11,679 --> 00:02:12,960
Far, far abroad.

38
00:02:13,519 --> 00:02:15,119
Abroad, near the border.

39
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:17,039
I sent him off with human traffickers.

40
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,440
By now, he's probably in some casino

41
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,159
serving drinks nonstop.

42
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,400
In one of those casinos

43
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:24,079
where bombings are
happening right now.

44
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,039
Aunt Khae!

45
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,480
As for you, it was even easier.

46
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:30,880
I just used someone else
to do the dirty work.

47
00:02:31,119 --> 00:02:33,679
I know that vengeance is like fire.

48
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:36,280
A fire that can kill a person.

49
00:02:37,519 --> 00:02:38,920
Even if you're certain

50
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:39,719
Saturn

51
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:41,880
had a part in your brother's suicide

52
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:44,000
there's absolutely nothing
you can do to him.

53
00:02:44,519 --> 00:02:45,400
So does that mean

54
00:02:46,119 --> 00:02:47,360
a terrible person like him

55
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,599
won't have to face any consequences

56
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:49,960
for what he's done?

57
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,599
No.

58
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:55,760
I won't let him get off that easily.

59
00:02:56,679 --> 00:02:57,760
I will get my revenge.

60
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,639
He must suffer exactly as he deserves.

61
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:04,840
If you truly want revenge

62
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,599
I might have a way.

63
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,400
How?

64
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:11,800
This Saturday

65
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,920
is the birthday anniversary

66
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:13,840
of that Dao Kang Fah.

67
00:03:15,199 --> 00:03:17,280
Saturn will be the main organizer.

68
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,400
If you want to get your hands on him

69
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:20,960
it shouldn't be hard.

70
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,000
Aunt Khae.

71
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:30,760
You intentionally manipulated him,
didn't you?

72
00:03:31,559 --> 00:03:32,480
Because you knew

73
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,199
that the main organizer that day was me,

74
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,760
Not Saturn

75
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,400
Lookkai.

76
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,679
Does this mean you knew
about all of this all along?

77
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,760
Then why did you do this to me?

78
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,880
Have I ever done anything to hurt you?

79
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,039
P'Dao

80
00:03:48,239 --> 00:03:49,000
I'm so sorry.

81
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,599
If everything you said is true

82
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:55,599
That means

83
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:57,360
that waiter was

84
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,400
Yes.

85
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,800
Now you're catching on.

86
00:04:02,239 --> 00:04:04,239
That was Pakin.

87
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:36,760
Hurry up!

88
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,079
Hurry and get him in the car

89
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,039
Before anyone sees us.

90
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,440
So Aunt Khae

91
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,280
really intended to manipulate

92
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,960
all of us this whole time.

93
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:14,679
Aunt Khae, how could you do this?

94
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,320
Even though Grandmother

95
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,559
my father

96
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,559
and my mother

97
00:05:19,679 --> 00:05:20,320
loved you.

98
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,639
They trusted you.

99
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,159
They took care of you

100
00:05:23,159 --> 00:05:24,280
and Lookkai your whole lives.

101
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,880
Took care of us? Took care of what?!

102
00:05:26,039 --> 00:05:27,280
Who took care of whom?

103
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:27,920
I was the only one

104
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,559
taking care of all of you!

105
00:05:28,559 --> 00:05:29,559
From your grandparents' generation

106
00:05:29,559 --> 00:05:31,360
to your parents,
all the way down to you!

107
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,480
Tell me, who does all
the work at this hotel?

108
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,400
It's only me!

109
00:05:34,519 --> 00:05:36,000
Who made this hotel famous?

110
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,320
Who made this hotel expand?

111
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:38,519
It was me, wasn't it?!

112
00:05:38,599 --> 00:05:39,079
And you people

113
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,480
did you ever think about repaying me

114
00:05:40,599 --> 00:05:41,559
Just tossing me scraps

115
00:05:41,559 --> 00:05:42,440
of money every month!

116
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,239
Is that supposed to be enough?!

117
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,079
You left me with no choice.

118
00:05:45,679 --> 00:05:47,239
If all of you just died

119
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,320
there would be no one
to inherit the fortune

120
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,360
but me and my child.

121
00:05:50,039 --> 00:05:51,119
Even if our bloodline traces back

122
00:05:51,119 --> 00:05:52,679
as distant relatives

123
00:05:52,679 --> 00:05:54,079
it's still just me and my child left.

124
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:56,039
I will definitely get this inheritance.

125
00:05:56,599 --> 00:05:58,920
Do you really intend to kill us, Auntie?

126
00:06:00,039 --> 00:06:01,199
You are so stupid.

127
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,400
Did you really think your parents

128
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:04,079
died in an accident?

129
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,480
What a fool.

130
00:06:06,039 --> 00:06:07,639
You will pay for this.

131
00:06:08,159 --> 00:06:08,960
I'm going to tell

132
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,079
Grandmother everything!

133
00:06:11,079 --> 00:06:11,920
Too bad.

134
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,880
It's too late for that.

135
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:27,239
What do you mean it's too late?

136
00:06:27,239 --> 00:06:29,199
You're all so stupid.

137
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,239
Couldn't you tell?

138
00:06:30,239 --> 00:06:32,480
That Lawyer Nod works for me.

139
00:06:32,679 --> 00:06:34,199
By now, Lawyer Nod is already with

140
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:35,960
that bitch Dao Kang Fah at the hospital.

141
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:36,840
What?!

142
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:43,119
Stop right there!

143
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,039
What else are you
planning to do, Auntie?

144
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:48,559
I already told you.

145
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:50,400
That everything is far too gone

146
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:52,000
to be fixed.

147
00:06:58,320 --> 00:06:59,000
Who the hell is that?

148
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:00,760
My name is Pakin.

149
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:03,480
Pakin.

150
00:07:04,119 --> 00:07:05,119
You know me?

151
00:07:06,199 --> 00:07:07,119
No, no.

152
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:09,960
Then who is that woman?

153
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:11,000
What did she do to you

154
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:12,719
that makes you want to kill her?

155
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:14,920
You bastard.

156
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,280
Tell me everything!

157
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:18,480
Mom!

158
00:07:19,119 --> 00:07:20,119
Don't hurt P'Dao!

159
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,280
Listen here.

160
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,719
Lookkai, have you forgotten

161
00:07:22,719 --> 00:07:24,519
what these two 'Daos' did to you?

162
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,960
It was only P'Saturn who did that to me.

163
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,840
P'Venus has nothing to do with it!

164
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,119
But they're siblings!

165
00:07:30,119 --> 00:07:31,239
They must be exactly the same!

166
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:32,280
That's not true

167
00:07:32,679 --> 00:07:34,280
Saturn and I are not the same.

168
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,599
Venus is right.

169
00:07:38,599 --> 00:07:39,760
You can't just lump
everything together.

170
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,119
You can't take out all
your anger and hatred

171
00:07:41,559 --> 00:07:43,440
on everyone else like this,
Khun Khaeng Khae.

172
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,880
You just won't stop meddling, will you

173
00:07:45,039 --> 00:07:45,880
Mavin?

174
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,800
If you take one more step

175
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,960
I will shoot Venus

176
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:50,760
How about this?

177
00:07:51,599 --> 00:07:53,199
To make everything easier

178
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,159
you walk over to the cliff and jump.

179
00:07:55,599 --> 00:07:57,599
Everyone will just think
you committed suicide.

180
00:07:58,559 --> 00:08:00,320
Why should I do as you say?

181
00:08:01,159 --> 00:08:03,639
So that others won't have to die.

182
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,760
Because if you don't do it

183
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:06,360
whether it's the people beside you

184
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,480
or far away, they will all die.

185
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,519
Khun Khaeng Khae.

186
00:08:10,239 --> 00:08:11,079
Please, listen to me.

187
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,199
Stop this.

188
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:14,159
And turn yourself in.

189
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:16,359
No way in hell.

190
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,760
If you're going to do anything to P'Dao

191
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,159
you'll have to do it to me first.

192
00:08:26,319 --> 00:08:26,960
Lookkai!

193
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:28,039
Don't do this!

194
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:29,760
It's dangerous, step aside!

195
00:08:30,159 --> 00:08:31,000
You stupid child!

196
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,000
Don't think I wouldn't dare!

197
00:08:34,439 --> 00:08:36,319
I will kill anyone who gets in my way!

198
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:37,199
Do it, Mom.

199
00:08:38,399 --> 00:08:40,039
Consider it paying for the sins

200
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,800
that I committed alongside you.

201
00:08:43,119 --> 00:08:44,359
You really are stupid.

202
00:08:45,359 --> 00:08:46,039
Do you know

203
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,239
that I did all of this for us?!

204
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,439
Yet you still choose them over me!

205
00:08:51,439 --> 00:08:53,079
Then go be with them!

206
00:08:53,079 --> 00:08:53,520
Go!

207
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:54,239
Khun Khaeng Khae!

208
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,279
Mom!

209
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:56,239
Khun Mavin!

210
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,000
Get back!

211
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:03,119
Let go right now!

212
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:05,680
Lookkai!

213
00:09:07,439 --> 00:09:08,239
Lookkai!

214
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,319
Lookkai!

215
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,159
Lookkai!

216
00:09:12,319 --> 00:09:13,079
Lookkai!

217
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:14,840
Please stay with me, Lookkai.

218
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,279
Hang in there, Lookkai.

219
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,319
No!

220
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:18,119
No!

221
00:09:19,079 --> 00:09:20,319
Lookkai! / It wasn't me.

222
00:09:20,319 --> 00:09:21,199
It wasn't me.

223
00:09:21,359 --> 00:09:22,239
It wasn't me.

224
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:23,640
P'Mavin!

225
00:09:24,359 --> 00:09:25,239
Call an ambulance!

226
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:26,960
Please send an ambulance immediately!

227
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,680
Don't leave me, Lookkai.

228
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:30,000
Mom didn't do this to you.

229
00:09:30,319 --> 00:09:30,600
No.

230
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:31,880
No.

231
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:33,279
I didn't do it.

232
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,840
Lookkai! Lookkai!

233
00:09:35,239 --> 00:09:35,800
Lookkai!

234
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:36,840
Lookkai, wake up!

235
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:37,439
Lookkai!

236
00:09:38,199 --> 00:09:38,800
Lookkai!

237
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:39,800
Wake up, Lookkai. Please wake up!

238
00:09:41,439 --> 00:09:42,439
I didn't do it.

239
00:09:43,319 --> 00:09:43,880
I didn't do it.

240
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:44,439
Khun Mavin, the ambulance!

241
00:09:46,479 --> 00:09:47,279
Lookkai.

242
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:48,399
My baby.

243
00:09:56,199 --> 00:09:57,880
Please be okay, Lookkai.

244
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,399
Wake up, Lookkai. Wake up!

245
00:10:04,039 --> 00:10:05,079
It wasn't me.

246
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,920
It wasn't me.

247
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,680
I didn't hurt my baby.

248
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:11,399
Khun Mavin, is the ambulance here yet?

249
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,640
I already called!

250
00:10:15,479 --> 00:10:17,600
Aunt Khae.
Aunt Khae, what are you doing?

251
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:18,800
Aunt Khae, don't!

252
00:10:19,199 --> 00:10:19,920
Aunt Khae!

253
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,359
Don't do it, Aunt Khae!

254
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:25,399
Khun Khaeng Khae!

255
00:10:26,399 --> 00:10:27,199
Aunt Khae!
